    "stdyInfo": {
      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Le but de cette étude est d'améliorer la connaissance concernant les fécondations in vitro mais également mieux comprendre la relation entre nombre d'embryons implantés/transfert de blastocystes et l’accouchement"
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "This study aims to improve knowledge regarding in vitro fertilisation and to better understand the relationship between the number of implanted embryos/blastocyst transfers and birth."
        }
      ],
